** Precision 2!c

Polish Club borrows this opening from Precision since it fits a 5-card major
forcing club system well.  We accommodate the Precision 2!c by slightly
shrinking its range to 11--14 HCP.

The bidding structure over 2!c resembles competitive bidding.  The 2!d relay
takes care of 4-card majors and game forcing long minors like a negative
double.  The 2NT puppet works like Lebensohl; responder passes 3!c as a
preemptive raise or bids again with FG options.  The rest are virtually
negative free bids.

We do not use 2NT as a balanced invitation in this system according to an
analysis on the Precision 2!c.

https://bridgewinners.com/article/view/opening-precision-2c/

