*** "Stayman" 2!d

This relay helps us find a 4-4 major fit, so we classify it as a Stayman.
Stayman also works better than a direct 3M when we have 4+ cards in each major.

The more clubs we have, the fewer points we need to bid this 2!d.  In other
words, we bid 2!d only if we can tolerate 3!c or force to game.

- *Constructive* = a 4-card major and a 9-card club fit
- *Invitational* = a 4-card major and a club fit or (54)+ in majors
- *Forcing to game* = any 4-card major or 5+!d

